          "reviewBody": "As a happy parent I feel proud to share that Carmel convent school has been successful in striking an appropriate balance between Academic and Co- Curricular activities. The teachers are Professional, caring and well- organized.\nThanks for taking initiative for online classes which shall help in better and productive utilisation of our time. we extend our heartfelt appreciation to the entire staff and special fo sister Anupama for their exceptional dedication and care towards our children education and well being.This institution isn't just a school . it's a bank full of learning and care and we are profoundly greatful to be part of this remarkable community great school. Which not only pushes children in academics but also in extra curricular activities.has a great infrastructure.I feel that my decision was right in sending my children to Carmel convent school.keep it up!I wish a great success to Carmel convent school.🙏🙏🙏💯👍",
